@startuml
title 正射影像拼接 DOM（复杂度 O(n³))

actor 质检员 as user
participant "前端" as front
participant "Gateway" as gw
participant "zrws-process" as svc
participant "Python AI" as ai
database "MySQL" as db
database "Redis" as cache
queue "RabbitMQ" as mq

== 提交拼接任务 ==
user -> front: 选择航拍照片集
front -> gw: POST /api/v1/processing/orthophoto
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_orthophoto_task
svc -> mq: 发送 orthophoto.task.created
mq -> svc: 消费任务

== 拼接管线 ==
svc -> db: [SQL] SELECT t_aerial_photo WHERE mission_id={id}
svc -> ai: [gRPC] stitchOrtho(photos[], cameraParams)
ai -> ai: 1. SIFT 特征提取与匹配
ai -> ai: 2. 相机位姿估计（SfM）
ai -> ai: 3. 稀疏点云 → 稠密点云
ai -> ai: 4. 网格重建 + 纹理映射
ai -> ai: 5. 正射校正 + 地理配准（GeoTIFF）
ai -> ai: 6. 瓦片金字塔生成
ai -> svc: 分块完成回调
svc -> svc: MinIO 存储拼接成果

== 进度推送 ==
loop 拼接进行中
    ai -> svc: 进度百分比 (每5%)
    svc -> cache: [Redis] PUBLISH stitch:progress:{taskId}
    svc -> gw: STOMP /topic/processing.progress
    gw -> front: 进度条更新
end

== 生成结果 ==
ai --> svc: StitchResult{ tifUrl, bounds, resolution, gsdCm }
svc -> db: [SQL] UPDATE t_orthophoto_task SET status='COMPLETED'
svc -> mq: 发送 orthophoto.completed
svc --> gw: R<OrthophotoResultVO>
gw --> front: 瓦片URL + 元数据
front -> front: Leaflet 加载正射影像底图

== 异常流程 ==
alt 照片不足
    svc --> gw: 400 最少需要 5 张有效照片
else SIFT 特征不足
    ai -> svc: 匹配点对 < 阈值
    svc --> gw: 400 重叠率不足，建议补拍
else 内存溢出
    ai -[#red]-> svc: OOM
    svc -> db: [SQL] UPDATE SET status='FAILED'
    svc --> gw: 500 数据量过大，请联系管理员
end

@enduml
